('33f45e5b-6633-816b-a1d2-f0446cb71b83', 'Auto Mercado × iRefill — In-Store Refill Expansion (Costa Rica)', 'Active', 'CH + Startup Shared', NULL, 'Not Scored', 'P1 — Act Now', 'High — >70%', '33d45e5b-6633-81a1-a5e6-ea3b077bb40a', 'Auto Mercado', 'UNDP partnership created a funded mandate for sustainable retail innovation. Auto Mercado leadership committed to piloting refill stations. iRefill machines available for LATAM deployment via CH commercial relationship.', NULL, NULL, 'Complete May 2026 machine delivery and installation at PDX Guayabos. Resolve dosing + QR compatibility. Execute June launch. Measure sell-through rates. If successful, activate Moravia location and build case for chain-wide expansion.', 'Live pilot as of Q2 2026. Pilot success = chain-wide expansion opportunity. UNDP funding covers software maintenance Year 1. Revenue model: 15% CH rev share on iRefill sales originated through CH-managed accounts. This brief was created to model the Auto Mercado × iRefill case in the new Opportunity Briefs structure.', 'Auto Mercado is Costa Rica’s leading premium supermarket with sustainability commitments and UNDP backing for a pilot. iRefill is the lowest-CapEx commercially-ready refill machine provider available to CH. The fit is confirmed by a live pilot in progress. UNDP funding removes financial friction. Auto Mercado has the location density and consumer profile for refill adoption.', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'UNDP partnership created a funded mandate for sustainable retail innovation. Auto Mercado leadership committed to piloting refill stations. iRefill machines available for LATAM deployment via CH commercial relationship.', 'https://www.notion.so/Auto-Mercado-iRefill-In-Store-Refill-Expansion-Costa-Rica-33f45e5b6633816ba1d2f0446cb71b83', '2026-04-11T20:35:00.000Z', '2026-04-11T20:35:00.000Z', '2026-04-11T20:35:00.000Z'),
